Simple yards/play analysis of 2021 NFL teams. (Learning multilevel models: yards_gained ~ (1|defteam) + (1|posteam) in lme4.)
(Scaled) Estimates based on all 2021 "normal" plays in regular season (removing penalties/STs/goal to go).
